snippet.title: Healthy Weapon - First Trailer
snippet.description:
Healthy Weapon is the first proper fighting game on Android that is truly made for touchscreen!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.regnsloja.healthyweapon

Challenge anyone sitting next to you to a brutal fruit smackdown!
Or just play single player in one of four modes: Arcade, Practice, Survival and the frustrating Unfair.

* Controls with touch devices in mind
* 2 player versus on the same device
* 6 charming main characters, 3 more unlockable
* Even more characters in a special mode...

* Wield variety of dangerous fruits and vegetables
